card.name: Fertile Ground
card.property: Enchant land Whenever enchanted land is tapped for mana, its controller adds an additional one mana of any color.

card.name: Indomitable Might
card.property: Flash Enchant creature Enchanted creature gets +3/+3. Enchanted creature's controller may have it assign its combat damage as though it weren't blocked.

card.name: Kenrith's Transformation
card.property: Enchant creature When Kenrith's Transformation enters the battlefield, draw a card. Enchanted creature loses all abilities and is a green Elk creature with base power and toughness 3/3. (It loses all other card types and creature types.)

card.name: Paradise Druid
card.property: Paradise Druid has hexproof as long as it's untapped. (It can't be the target of spells or abilities your opponents control.) {T}: Add one mana of any color.

card.name: Rishkar's Expertise
card.property: Draw cards equal to the greatest power among creatures you control. You may cast a spell with mana value 5 or less from your hand without paying its mana cost.

card.name: Sanctum Weaver
card.property: {T}: Add X mana of any one color, where X is the number of enchantments you control.

card.name: Setessan Champion
card.property: Constellation — Whenever an enchantment enters the battlefield under your control, put a +1/+1 counter on Setessan Champion and draw a card.

card.name: Snake Umbra
card.property: Enchant creature Enchanted creature gets +1/+1 and has "Whenever this creature deals damage to an opponent, you may draw a card." Umbra armor (If enchanted creature would be destroyed, instead remove all damage from it and destroy this Aura.)

card.name: Sylvan Ranger
card.property: When Sylvan Ranger enters the battlefield, you may search your library for a basic land card, reveal it, put it into your hand, then shuffle.

card.name: Utopia Sprawl
card.property: Enchant Forest As Utopia Sprawl enters the battlefield, choose a color. Whenever enchanted Forest is tapped for mana, its controller adds an additional one mana of the chosen color.

card.name: Verdant Embrace
card.property: Enchant creature Enchanted creature gets +3/+3 and has "At the beginning of each upkeep, create a 1/1 green Saproling creature token."

card.name: Warbriar Blessing
card.property: Enchant creature you control When Warbriar Blessing enters the battlefield, enchanted creature fights up to one target creature you don't control. (Each deals damage equal to its power to the other.) Enchanted creature gets +0/+2.

card.name: Glen Elendra Liege
card.property: Flying Other blue creatures you control get +1/+1. Other black creatures you control get +1/+1.

card.property: Flying When Halo Forager enters the battlefield, you may pay {X}. When you do, you may cast target instant or sorcery card with mana value X from a graveyard without paying its mana cost. If that spell would be put into a graveyard, exile it instead.

card.name: Jukai Naturalist
card.property: Lifelink Enchantment spells you cast cost {1} less to cast.

card.name: Nymris, Oona's Trickster
card.property: Flash Flying Whenever you cast your first spell during each opponent's turn, look at the top two cards of your library. Put one of those cards into your hand and the other into your graveyard.

card.property: Enchant creature Enchanted creature has flying. Whenever enchanted creature deals combat damage to a player, create that many 1/1 green Saproling creature tokens.

card.name: Siona, Captain of the Pyleas
card.property: When Siona, Captain of the Pyleas enters the battlefield, look at the top seven cards of your library. You may reveal an Aura card from among them and put it into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order. Whenever an Aura you control becomes attached to a creature you control, create a 1/1 white Human Soldier creature token.
